[[Translation:en/Manual/Cycle signal types]]


Set which type of signal should be cycled through when ctrl-clicking on a ready-built signal. Choose between cycling through all [[en/signal]] types, just the [[en/block signals]] types or only the [[en/path signals]] types.

0 = Block signals only
1 = Path signals only
2 = All

